item.title: Re: Misspelled page names
item.content:encoded:
I can't get on BvS to check it at this moment, but when they were introduced ( hence the page names ), they were spelt with two Ls, not one.

As far as I know, it hasn't changed, but I could be wrong.

(edit) It seems that it's been fixed on BvS now, so changing the page titles would be warranted.

item.title: Misspelled page names
item.content:encoded:
The Duelist's Eye and Duelist's Aura are both in the name of their pages. Since I don't know how to change the name of a page, all I can do is point it out. (I did correct the spelling within the pages, however.)

The Pages:

http://bvs.wikidot.com/items:duellist-s-aura
http://bvs.wikidot.com/items:duellist-s-eye

Note the extra "l" in both of them.
